{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":171201,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ら、ランス様……この気配は……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"L-Lord Rance... this presence...\""},{"lineNumber":171202,"originalJapaneseLine":"牢屋の奥から漂う濃厚な気配、","translatedEnglishLine":"A dense presence drifting from the back of the prison,"},{"lineNumber":171203,"originalJapaneseLine":"視線を巡らせるとそこにそれはいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"As I looked around, there it was."},{"lineNumber":171204,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":171205,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う、嘘！　魔人カミーラ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"N-No way! The demon, Camilla!?\""},{"lineNumber":171206,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんでこんな所に！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Why is she in a place like this!\""},{"lineNumber":171207,"originalJapaneseLine":"室内にいたのは、ケイブリスの恋人として","translatedEnglishLine":"The one inside the room was Camilla, treated with care as Kéibris' lover,"},{"lineNumber":171208,"originalJapaneseLine":"丁重に扱われている、囚われの身のカミーラだった。","translatedEnglishLine":"a captive Camilla."},{"lineNumber":171209,"originalJapaneseLine":"こちらに気づいているのか、いないのか、","translatedEnglishLine":"Whether she noticed us or not,"},{"lineNumber":171210,"originalJapaneseLine":"カミーラは顔色一つ変えない。","translatedEnglishLine":"Camilla did not change her expression at all."},{"lineNumber":171211,"originalJapaneseLine":"その瞳が、不意に動き、サテラに視線が向けられた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Suddenly, her eyes moved and she directed her gaze at Satera."},{"lineNumber":171212,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ホーネット派の奴ら、か」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Hornet faction, huh.\""},{"lineNumber":171213,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ケイブリスと戦いに来たか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You've come to fight Kéibris...\""},{"lineNumber":171214,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお、そうだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, that's right."},{"lineNumber":171215,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あいつが色々と邪魔だからな。","translatedEnglishLine":"Because that guy is a big obstacle."},{"lineNumber":171216,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ズバーッと殺してくるところだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I’m going to just stab through and kill him.\""},{"lineNumber":171217,"originalJapaneseLine":"「貴様……ランス……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You... Rance...\""},{"lineNumber":171218,"originalJapaneseLine":"「久しぶりだな、カミーラ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Long time no see, Camilla.\""},{"lineNumber":171219,"originalJapaneseLine":"（ここにいるということは……","translatedEnglishLine":"(The fact that she's here means..."},{"lineNumber":171220,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こいつもケイブリスと戦うつもり、か……）","translatedEnglishLine":"she also intends to fight Kéibris...)"} ,
{"lineNumber":171221,"originalJapaneseLine":"（人間の身で……","translatedEnglishLine":"(As a mere human..."},{"lineNumber":171222,"originalJapaneseLine":"　大それたことを……）","translatedEnglishLine":"...to do something so outrageous...)"},{"lineNumber":171223,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh...\""},{"lineNumber":171224,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わ、笑った……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"S-She smiled..."},{"lineNumber":171225,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんか好感触じゃないか、どう思う？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Feels like a good sign, don’t you think?\""},{"lineNumber":171226,"originalJapaneseLine":"「絶対に違うから、お願いだから刺激しないで」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Absolutely not, so please don't provoke her.\""},{"lineNumber":171227,"originalJapaneseLine":"（ケイブリスを倒す、か……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(To defeat Kéibris, huh...)"},{"lineNumber":171228,"originalJapaneseLine":"（私には……そんな勇気も行動力も、ないな……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(I don’t have that kind of courage or initiative...)"},{"lineNumber":171229,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むう……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Mmm...\""},

{"lineNumber":171230,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":171231,"originalJapaneseLine":"（しかし……以前散々レイプしたからな、","translatedEnglishLine":"(However... since I ravaged her thoroughly before,"},{"lineNumber":171232,"originalJapaneseLine":"　正直、怒り狂って向かってくるかと思ったが、","translatedEnglishLine":"to be honest, I thought she'd come raging at me,"},{"lineNumber":171233,"originalJapaneseLine":"　何かしてくる気配はないな……）","translatedEnglishLine":"but there’s no sign she intends to do anything...)"},{"lineNumber":171234,"originalJapaneseLine":"（まさか、本当に俺に惚れて……？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Could it be that she really fell for me...?)"},{"lineNumber":171235,"originalJapaneseLine":"（……いや、違う。","translatedEnglishLine":"(...No, that’s not it."},{"lineNumber":171236,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こいつ、ただ無気力なだけだ）","translatedEnglishLine":"She’s just apathetic.)"},{"lineNumber":171237,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし、どうしてカミーラがここに……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"But why is Camilla here...\""},{"lineNumber":171238,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔人ケイブリスのお気に入りなんだ、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"She’s the demon Kéibris' favorite,"},{"lineNumber":171239,"originalJapaneseLine":"　カミーラはな」","translatedEnglishLine":"Camilla.\""},{"lineNumber":171240,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ほほう、それなら人質に取れば……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh? Then maybe we could take her hostage...\""},{"lineNumber":171241,"originalJapaneseLine":"「馬鹿言わないでよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Don’t be stupid!"},{"lineNumber":171242,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そんなこと出来ると思ってるの！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Do you really think that’s possible!?\""},{"lineNumber":171243,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……無理そうだな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Looks impossible.\""},{"lineNumber":171244,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おい、カミーラ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey, Camilla."},{"lineNumber":171245,"originalJapaneseLine":"　サテラ達は今からケイブリスを倒す。","translatedEnglishLine":"Satera and the others are going to defeat Kéibris now."},{"lineNumber":171246,"originalJapaneseLine":"　退くならここは無視しよう」","translatedEnglishLine":"If you step aside, we'll ignore this place.\""},{"lineNumber":171247,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だが、もしも邪魔すると言うのなら……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"But if you say you’ll interfere...\""},{"lineNumber":171248,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":171249,"originalJapaneseLine":"殺気立つサテラにも興味なさそうに、","translatedEnglishLine":"Camilla seemed uninterested even in the threatening Satera,"},{"lineNumber":171250,"originalJapaneseLine":"スイッとカミーラは視線を逸らした。","translatedEnglishLine":"and smoothly averted her gaze."},{"lineNumber":171251,"originalJapaneseLine":"その視線の先を見るようにと伝えるように。","translatedEnglishLine":"As if signaling to look in the direction of her gaze."},{"lineNumber":171252,"originalJapaneseLine":"「行け」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Go.\""},{"lineNumber":171253,"originalJapaneseLine":"「な、なんだと？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-What did you say?\""},{"lineNumber":171254,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ケイブリスはこの部屋を出て左の方向にいる筈だ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kéibris should be to the left after leaving this room.\""},{"lineNumber":171255,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……どういうつもりだ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...What do you mean by that?\""},{"lineNumber":171256,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":171257,"originalJapaneseLine":"言うべきはもうないということか、","translatedEnglishLine":"As if to say there’s nothing more to say,"},{"lineNumber":171258,"originalJapaneseLine":"カミーラは黙したまま何も語らない。","translatedEnglishLine":"Camilla remained silent and said nothing."},{"lineNumber":171259,"originalJapaneseLine":"「私達と戦う気はない。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"She has no intention of fighting us."},{"lineNumber":171260,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いいえ、戦う理由がないのでしょう」","translatedEnglishLine":"No, she probably has no reason to fight.\""}]}

